arStrings.szText: For a hundred generations, Hell itself imprisoned Father Inarius, but they could not break him. He cast off his infernal shackles and returned to us.
Very pious, excited. Telling a grand tale about her benefactor, the angel Inarius.
And now he will guide the faithful along the path of deliverance.
